%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Passengers%20Claim%20Stuck%20In%20Phuket%20For%2080%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20100%20New%20Delhi-bound%20passengers%20of%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20have%20been%20stranded%20in%20Thailand's%20Phuket%20for%20over%2080%20hours%20now%20after%20several%20delays%20due%20to%20technical%20faults%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20posts%20put%20out%20by%20passengers%20on%20social%20media.%20NDTV%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20airline%20for%20a%20response%2C%20but%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20get%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20passengers%2C%20the%20flight%20was%20scheduled%20to%20take%20off%20for%20Delhi%20on%20the%20night%20of%20November%2016.%20But%20the%20airline's%20representatives%20informed%20the%20passengers%20of%20a%20six-hour%20delay%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20fault.%20The%20passengers%20allege%20that%20after%20being%20made%20to%20wait%20for%20hours%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20board%20the%20plane%2C%20only%20to%20be%20deboarded%20an%20hour%20later.%20The%20flight%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20passengers%20included%20elderly%20and%20children.%20The%20next%20the%20plane%20was%20prepped%20for%20a%20flight.%20The%20passengers%20say%20they%20were%20told%20that%20it%20was%20the%20same%20plane%2C%20but%20the%20fault%20had%20been%20fixed.%20The%20plane%20took%20off%20and%20about%20two-and-a-half%20hours%20after%20take-off%2C%20it%20landed%20back%20at%20Phuket%20and%20the%20passengers%20were%20again%20told%20that%20there%20was%20a%20technical%20fault%20.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20passengers%20have%20been%20stuck%20at%20Phuket.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732011660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fbg4hsr3g_air-india-a350-_625x300_01_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-passengers-claim-stuck-in-phuket-for-80-hours-7055085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20100%20New%20Delhi-bound%20passengers%20of%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20have%20been%20stranded%20in%20Thailand's%20Phuket%20for%20over%2080%20hours%20now%20after%20several%20delays%20due%20to%20technical%20faults%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20posts%20put%20out%20by%20passengers%20on%20social%20media%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20Responds%20To%20Biden's%20Missile%20Approval%20By%20Changing%20Nuclear%20Doctrine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20West%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%20signed%20a%20decree%20broadening%20the%20scope%20of%20Moscow%20using%20nuclear%20weapons%20on%20a%20non-nuclear%20state%20if%20it%20is%20supported%20by%20nuclear%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20comes%20on%20the%201%2C000th%20day%20of%20Russia%20invading%20Ukraine%2C%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20gave%20Ukraine%20permission%20to%20use%20its%20long-range%20missiles%20to%20strike%20deeper%20in%20Russian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20had%20made%20a%20significant%20policy%20change%2C%20allowing%20Ukraine%20to%20use%20US-made%20ATACMS%20missiles%20to%20strike%20targets%20inside%20Russia%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20came%20just%20two%20months%20before%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20hands%20over%20power%20to%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20expressed%20scepticism%20about%20US%20military%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20vowed%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20defeat%20Ukraine%2C%20saying%20Western%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20would%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20conflict%20and%20that%20western%20aid%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20affect%20the%20outcome%20of%20our%20operation.%20It%20continues%2C%20and%20will%20be%20completed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20military%20operation%20against%20Kyiv%20continues%2C%26q