20died%20or%20have%20been%20grievously%20injured%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20grim%20reality%20of%20the%20deadliest%20war%20of%20the%2021st%20Century%2C%20cities%2C%20towns%2C%20and%20villages%20in%20Ukraine%20have%20been%20devastated%20and%20now%20lie%20in%20ruin.%20The%20loss%20of%20human%20life%20and%20material%20wealth%20keep%20mounting%20in%20a%20never-ending%20series%20of%20heartbreaking%20stories%20emerging%20from%20the%20war-torn%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20have%20diminishing%20populations%20and%20have%20been%20struggling%20from%20even%20before%20the%20war.%20The%20staggering%20death%20count%20due%20to%20the%20war%20will%20thereby%20have%20far-reaching%20demographic%20implications%20for%20both%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732011600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F55ha3a7_russian-nuclear-missiles-russia-nukes-istock_625x300_10_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-okays-broader-use-of-nuclear-weapons-as-russia-marks-1-000-days-of-ukraine-war-7054872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kremlin%20vowed%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20defeat%20Ukraine%2C%20saying%20Western%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20would%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-okays-broader-use-of-nuclear-weapons-as-russia-marks-1-000-days-of-ukraine-war-7054872%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20and%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20want%20to%20'delete'%20parts%20of%20the%20US%20government.%20It%20won't%20be%20easy.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20and%20Vivek%20on%20a%20delete%20button%20with%20Capitol%20building.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673bc4ddede4eeae39