%20Kevin%20Kosar%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20conservative%20think%20tank%20the%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-department-of-government-efficiency-donald-trump-ramaswamy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExperts%20previously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20DOGE's%20stated%20goal%20of%20cutting%20%242%20trillion%20from%20the%20federal%20budget%20is%20unrealistic%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20the%20hope%20to%20eliminate%20agencies%20whole%20cloth%20is%20similarly%20far-fetched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22265e84ea-1920-4b64-8158-16ebba7d0ad5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20close%20examination%20of%20government%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20during%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-doge-wants-to-delete-entire-federal-agencies-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunday%20appearance%20on%20Fox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20expects%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20agencies%20to%20be%20deleted%20outright%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20did%20not%20specify%20which%20particular%20departments%20he'd%20like%20to%20eliminate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20mass%20reductions%20in%20force%20in%20areas%20of%20the%20federal%20government%20that%20are%20bloated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20running%20for%20the%202024%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20Ramaswamy%20flirted%20with%20cutting%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%2C%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%2C%20and%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Alcohol%2C%20Firearms%2C%20and%20Tobacco%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F13%2Fus%2Ftrump-close-department-of-education.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20interest%20in%20doing%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20efforts%20would%20be%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20achieve%20politically%2C%20and%20it%20would%20also%20present%20a%20new%20dilemma%3A%20What%20agency%20would%20take%20on%20the%20roles%20of%20another%20if%20it%20were%20to%20be%20axed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20obvious%20question%20becomes%2C%20if%20the%20IRS%20were%20abolished%2C%20does%20that%20mean%20that%20they're%20abolishing%20the%20income%20tax%3F%26quot%3B%20Mordecai%20Lee%2C%20a%20professor%20emeritus%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Milwaukee%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOr%20does%20it%20mean%20that%20a%20different%20federal%20agency%20will%20assume%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20collecting%20income%20taxes%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20the%20latter%2C%20then%20you're%20probably%20just%20sort%20of%20shuffling%20boxes%20in%20an%20organization%20chart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275c49e96-fa27-4e40-82e3-8178535353a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20potential%20roadblocks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPresidents%20aren't%20able%20to%20eliminate%20agencies%20or%20Cabinet%20departments%20on%20their%20own%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20Trump%20couldn't%20independently%20turn%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy's%20advice%20into%20reality.%20Previous%20presidents%20have%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20departments%2C%20largely%20because%20they%20haven't%20had%20Congress'%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20smaller%2C%20lesser%20known%20agencies%20are%20almost%20inevitably%20%E2%80%94%20they%20exist%20because%20of%20an%20act%20of%20law.%20So%20getting%20rid%20of%20them%20means%20passing%20a%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Kosar%20said.%20Presidents%20can%20get%20rid%20of%20administrative%20units%20in%20an%20agency%20that%20aren't%20enshrined%20in%20legislation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20not%20much%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224262%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20at%20a%20House%20Republicans%20Conference%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673ba838192f525898593c61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222841%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20aiming%20to%20reduce%20the%20size%20of%20the%20federal%20government%20in%20his%20second%20term.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Robbert-Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20president%20can't%20'delete'%20departments%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20almost%20all%20of%20government's%20subunits.%20That%20would%20require%20Congress%20to%20act%2C%20and%20even%20a%20Republican-controlled%20Congress%20is%20going%20to%20be%20reluctant%20to%20take%20such%20a%20large%20wrecking%20ball%20to%20government's%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20Donald%20Kettl%2C%20former%20dean%20of%20the%20school%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElaine%20Kamarck%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20nonpartisan%20Brookings%20Institute%20who%20led%20efforts%20to%20reform%20the%20federal%20government%20under%20former%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20said%20that%20there's%20little%20appetite%20among%20lawmakers%20to%20cut%20out%20entire%20agencies%2C%20and%20that%20doing%20so%20would%20%26quot%3Bblow%20up%20in%20their%20faces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20those%20areas%20where%20everybody%20likes%20it%20in%20the%20macro%20and%20the%20minute%20you%20discuss%20cutting%20down%20a%20department%2C%20people%20say%2C%20'Wait%20a%20minute%3F%20Who%20is%20gonna%20do%20this%3F%20Who%20is%20gonna%20do%20that%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20The%20complicated%20process%20of%20firing%20federal%20employees%20is%20another%20roadblock%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOGE%20could%20try%20to%20reorganize%20the%20government%20by%20moving%20programs%20from%20one%20agency%20to%20another%2C%20and%20deleting%20a%20bureaucratic%20body%20in%20the%20process.%20For%20instance%2C%20both%20Kosar%20and%20Kamarck%20said%20the%20DOGE%20could%20recommend%20moving%20student%20loans%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20to%20another%20governmental%20body%2C%20and%20then%20deleting%20the%20Department%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20abolish%20an%20agency%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20not%20abolishing%20the%20programs%20and%20the%20governmental%20authority%20that%20goes%20with%20it%2C%20you're%20not%20really%20downsizing%20the%20government%20in%20a%20significant%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Kosar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKettl%20said%20that%20any%20effort%20to%20delete%20the%20functions%20of%20a%20department%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20even%20bigger%20battle%26quot%3B%20than%20trying%20to%20delete%20a%20department%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20calculus%20is%20complicated%2C%20the%20experts%20said.%20Republicans%20risk%20angering%20constituents%20if%20they%20agree%20to%20slash%20agencies%20that%20administer%20popular%20programs%2C%20but%20also%20risk%20failing%20to%20help%20Trump%20follow%20through%20on%20a%20splashy%20campaign%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20said%20that%20the%20current%20size%20of%20the%20US%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20reflection%20of%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFarmers%20like%20having%20a%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20this%20commission%20were%20to%20recommend%20abolishing%20the%20USDA.%20Farmers%20would%20be%20against%20it%2C%20and%20senators%20from%20farm%20states%20would%20be%20against%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConservative%20activists%20for%20decades%20have%20sought%20to%20enact%20large-scale%20cuts%20to%20myriad%20government%20agencies%2C%20and%20they%20largely%20see%20Trump's%20second%20term%20as%20a%20prime%20opportunity%20to%20push%20GOP%20lawmakers%20on%20stances%20they've%20long%20advocated%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20they%20didn't%20manage%20to%20nix%20at%20least%20one%20agency.%20Whether%20it's%20an%20agency%20most%20Americans%20have%20ever%20heard%20of%20is%20a%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Kosar%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20these%20things.%20Having%20made%20it%20a%20big%20promise%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20that%20comes%20with%20it%2C%20not%20to%20fail.%20Especially%20because%20you%20have%20single%20party%20control%20of%20Congress%20and%20the%20presidency%2C%20the%20pressure%20is%20all%20the%20higher.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-ramaswamy-trump-doge-government-agencies-reform-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732011542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673bc519192f5258985945b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-ramaswamy-trump-doge-government-agencies-reform-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20DOGE's%20goal%20of%20cutting%20%242%20trillion%20from%20the%20federal%20budget%20is%20unrealistic%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20the%20hope%20to%20delete%20agencies%20is%20similarly%20far-fetched.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky%2CJohn%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-ramaswamy-trump-doge-government-agencies-reform-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20president%20Vladimir%20Putin%20to%20visit%20India%20soon%2C%20says%20Kremlin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732011208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115449336%2Cimgsize-745602.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frussian-president-vladimir-putin-to-visit