for%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20update%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20September%20opinion%20piece%20that%20ran%20in%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20Kennedy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrump-can-make-america-healthy-again-rfk-jr-reforms-chronic-disease-crisis-a9b4b8c0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bprohibit%26quot%3B%20members%20of%20the%20dietary%20guidelines%20advisory%20committee%20from%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20money%20from%20food%20or%20drug%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20advisory%20committee%2C%20largely%20composed%20of%20academic%20nutrition%20experts%2C%20does%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dietaryguidelines.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-06%2F2025_DGAC_Disclosures_508c.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustry%20disclosures%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20the%20final%20say%20on%20guidelines%3B%20the%20committee%20only%20reviews%20the%20science%20behind%20federal%20health%20recommendations.%20The%20task%20of%20writing%20up%20the%20guidelines%20will%20fall%20to%20federal%20employees%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20as%20well%20as%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20an%20agency%20Kennedy%20would%20not%20oversee%20in%20his%20new%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Kennedy's%20proposed%20shake-up%20is%20welcome%20news%20to%20companies%20like%20Zero%20Acre%2C%20a%20line%20of%20alternative%20cooking%20oils%20used%20by%20Chipotle%20and%20Shake%20Shack.%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20Jeff%20Nobbs%20told%20Business%20Insider%20there's%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20that%20feels%20strange%26quot%3B%20about%20how%20the%20dietary%20guidelines%20are%20written%2C%20including%20a%20mention%20of%20vegetable%20oil%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcore%20element%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20healthy%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20we%20can%20remove%20any%20conflicts%20of%20interest%20so%20that%20we%20just%20have%20a%20direct%20line%20from%20what%20the%20science%20is%20saying%20to%20what%20dietary%20guidelines%20and%20policy%20and%20regulations%20are%20actually%20implemented%2C%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Nobbs%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20has%20loudly%20campaigned%20against%20%26quot%3Bseed%20oils%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20canola%20and%20soybean%20oil%20that's%20often%20used%20in%20fryers%20and%20processed%20foods%2C%20and%20even%20developed%20a%20line%20of%20red%20t-shirts%20and%20hats%20dedicated%20to%20%26quot%3BMake%20frying%20oil%20tallow%20again.%26quot%3B%20Experts%20say%20the%20internet%20furor%20around%20%26quot%3Bseed%20oils%26quot%3B%20is%20unscientific%20and%20sidesteps%20more%20important%20forces%20shaping%20what%20we%20eat%20and%20how%20it%20influences%20health%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%2C%20wearing%20an%20apron%20and%20holding%20a%20container%20of%20fries%2C%20next%20to%20a%20McDonald's%20employee%20in%20the%20kitchen%20of%20a%20Pennsylvania%20McDonald's.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b947aede4eeae39283b60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20served%20fries%20at%20a%20Pennsylvania%20McDonald's%20in%20October%20as%20part%20of%20a%20staged%20event%20on%20his%20campaign%20trail.%3Cp%3EDoug%20Mills-Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20crusade%20against%20Big%20Food%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F15%2Fhealth%2Frfk-big-food-artificial-dyes-trump.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20up%20against%20Trump's%20pro-corporation%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though.%20It%20seems%20at%20odds%20with%20some%20of%20the%20president-elect's%20favorite%20food%20groups%2C%20like%20KFC%20and%20McDonald's.%20Kennedy%20was%20recently%20photographed%20smiling%20and%20picking%20up%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20Big%20Mac%20on%20Trump's%20campaign%20plane%2C%20sharing%20a%20table%20with%20Trump%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20Jr.%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDonaldJTrumpJr%2Fstatus%2F1858136498530374074%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoked%20in%20an%20accompanying%20X%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Healthy%20Again%20starts%20TOMORROW.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcampaign-election-staff-diet-coke-mcdonalds-cigarette-harris-trump-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECampaign%20food%20is%20always%20bad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20food%20that%20goes%20onto%20that%20airplane%20is%20like%20just%20poison%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20told%20podcaster%20Joe%20Polish.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20choice%20between%20%E2%80%94%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20choice%2C%20you're%20either%20given%20KFC%20or%20Big%20Macs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218d33eac-7be1-4e02-a276-d44642714d06%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight-loss%20companies%20could%20get%20more%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20cost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20focus%20on%20holistic%20chronic%20disease%20care%2C%20including%20obesity%20care%2C%20could%20see%20a%20renewed%20funding%20rush%20to%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-investors-torn-on-trump-second-term-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELikely%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20federal%20Medicaid%20funding%20under%20a%20second%20Trump%20administration%20and%20potential%20crackdowns%20on%20weight-loss%20drugs%20may%20limit%20patient%20access%20to%20that%20care%2C%20however%2C%20said%20obesity%20care%20startup%20Knownwell%20CEO%20Brooke%20Boyarsky%20Pratt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20has%20previously%20criticized%20government%20efforts%20to%20pay%20for%20costly%20GLP-1%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20spending%20%241%2C600%20a%20month%20on%20this%20drug.%20There's%20a%20bill%20right%20now%20before%20Congress%20that%20will%20make%20it%20available%20to%20everybody%20who%20is%20overweight%2C%20which%20is%2074%25%20of%20the%20American%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20October%20Fox%20News%20appearance.%20%26quot%3BThat%20alone%20will%20cost%20%243%20trillion%20a%20year.%20If%20we%20spend%20about%20one-fifth%20of%20that%20giving%20good%20food%2C%20three%20meals%20a%20day%20to%20every%20man%2C%20woman%2C%20and%20child%20in%20our%20country%2C%20we%20can%20solve%20the%20obesity%20and%20diabetes%20epidemic%20overnight%20for%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20Kennedy%20referenced%2C%20the%20Treat%20and%20Reduce%20Obesity%20Act%2C%20would%20allow%20Medicare%20to%20cover%20GLP-1s%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20a%20move%20Kennedy%20has%20indicated%20he%20would%20oppose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brooke%20Boyarsky%20Pratt%2C%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Knownwell.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c8615764df161125a13dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKnownwell%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Brooke%20Boyarsky%20Pratt.%3Cp%3EKnownwell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPratt%20also%20said%20she's%20concerned%20that%20Kennedy's%20battle%20with%20the%20FDA%20could%20inhibit%20FDA%20oversight%20of%20compounding%20pharmacies%20making%20copycat%20versions%20of%20GLP-1%20drugs.%20Knownwell%20prescribes%20GLP-1s%20for%20its%20patients%20where%20appropriate%20but%20doesn't%20prescribe%20compounded%20versions%2C%20which%20aren't%20FDA-approved%2C%20Pratt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegally%2C%20compounding%20pharmacies%20are%20only%20allowed%20to%20sell%20drug%20recreations%20when%20those%20drugs%20are%20in%20shortage%2C%20a%20regulation%20that's%20enforced%20by%20the%20FDA.%20If%20Kennedy%20decides%20to%20slash%20the%20FDA's%20workforce%20and%20go%20after%20Big%20Pharma%2C%20it's%20unclear%20how%20that%20enforcement%20might%20be%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f66d9311-1050-4d4b-a84b-ec307a949aad%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrugmakers%20and%20their%20benefactors%20will%20be%20under%20pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20Kennedy's%20nomination%20hit%20drugmakers%20across%20the%20board%2C%20particularly%20vaccine%20manufacturers.%20Covid-19%20vaccine%20maker%20Moderna%20saw%20the%20sharpest%20dip%2C%20with%20its%20shares%20falling%20nearly%206%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading%20following%20the%20announcement.%20(Its%20stock%20has%20since%20rebounded.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20biopharma%20startups%20and%20investors%2C%20including%20those%20focused%20on%20chronic%20diseases%2C%20are%20getting%20nervous.%20John%20Stanford%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20Incubate%20Coalition%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20group%20of%20life-sciences%20investors%2C%20said%20investors%20are%20worried%20about%20diminishing%20exits%20if%20large%20drug%20companies%20have%20fewer%20funds%20to%20make%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20large%20manufacturers%20are%20hit%20by%20bad%20policy%2C%20it%20has%20immediate%20consequences%20on%20our%20ability%20to%20exit%20our%20funds%20and%20redeploy%20capital%2C%20and%20we're%20already%20seeing%20that%20play%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20spooks%20everybody%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20have%20a%20downstream%20effect%20on%20the%20investment%20community%20in%20the%20early-stage%20ecosystem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pick-rfk-jr-impact-ozempic-weight-loss-food-nutrition-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732010462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b88e2fa0140cdd5641626%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pick-rfk-jr-impact-ozempic-weight-loss-food-nutrition-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kennedy%20has%20promised%20to%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Healthy%20Again%26quot%3B%20by%20tackling%20obesity%20with%20nutrition.%20Here's%20how%20he%20could%20rattle%20the%20surging%20weight-loss%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence%2CHilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pick-rfk-jr-impact-ozempic-weight-loss-food-nutrition-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Delhi's%20AQI%20Was%20494%20Today%20But%20International%20Monitor%20Said%201%2C600%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20air%20quality%20remained%20severely%20toxic%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20the%20overall%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%2C%20which%20measures%20pollutants%2C%20spiked%20to%20494.%20According%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20of%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%20data%2C%20most%20of%20the%20monitoring%20stations%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20500%2C%20forcing%20all%20schools%20across%20Delhi-NCR%20to%20go%20online.%20However%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20international%20monitoring%20app%2C%20IQAir%2C%20showed%20Delhi's%20AQI%20at%201%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Delhi's%20AQI%20Was%20494%20but%20IQAir%20showed%201%2C600%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20countries%20have%20different%20standards%20for%20measuring%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-remains-toxic-dense-fog-lowers-visibility-trains-delayed-7052147%5C%22%3Eair%20quality%20index%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20varies%20from%20country%20to%20country%2C%20depending%20on%20pollutants%20and%20their%20measuring%20scale.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20PM%202.5%20is%2060%2C%20while%20in%20some%20countries%2C%20that%20have%20adopted%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20standard%2C%20is%20five%20or%20ten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20India's%20AQI%20has%20been%20capped%20at%20500%20-%20which%20means%20that%20an%20air%20quality%20index%20bigger%20than%20that%20is%20a%20big%20warning%20that%20the%20level%20of%20pollution%20is%20extremely%20severe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CPCB%2C%20an%20AQI%20between%200%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20good%2C%2051%20and%20100%20satisfactory%2C%20101%20and%20200%20moderate%2C%20201%20and%20300%20poor%2C%20301%20and%20400%20very%20poor%2C%20401%20and%20450%20severe%2C%20and%20above%20450%20to%20500%20is%20severe-plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20IQAir%20-%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20US%20model%20developed%20by%20the%20country's%20Environment%20Protection%20Agency%2C%20has%20'hazardous'%20as%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20scale%20(over%20500).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20international%20agencies%20monitor%20India's%20AQI%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20agencies%20such%20as%20IQAir%20have%20installed%20sensors%20at%20some%20places%20across%20Delhi-NCR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clear%20information%20on%20whether%20the%20sensors%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20right%20place%20with%20the%20standard%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20monitor's%20AQI%20should%20we%20follow%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20particular%20right%20or%20wrong%20monitor%2C%20in%20India%2C%20citizens%20should%20consider%20the%20AQI%20released%20by%20the%20CPCB%20-%20which%20has%2040%20stations%20across%20Delhi-NCR%20for%20assessing%20pollution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi's%20air%20remains%20toxic%2C%20GRAP%204%20imposed%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-crisis-need-of-the-hour-delhi-government-writes-to-centre-for-artificial-rain-7054508%5C%22%3Eair%20quality%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20%3C%2Fa%3Eentered%20the%20'severe%20plus'%20category%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20imposed%20Stage%204%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%2C%20an%20anti-pollution%20plan%20-%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20first%20three%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%2C%20a%20ban%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20Delhi-registered%20BS-IV%20or%20older%20diesel%20medium%20and%20heavy%20goods%20vehicles.%20All%20trucks%20and%20light%20commercial%20vehicles%20registered%20outside%20Delhi%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20except%20for%20those%20carrying%20essential%20commodities%20or%20providing%20essential%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20public%20and%20private%20offices%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20work%20at%2050%20per%20cent%20capacity%20and%20the%20rest%20have%20been%20recommended%20to%20work%20from%20home.%20All%20schools%20have%20been%20either%20closed%20or%20gone%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732009860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fr7695oo_delhi-air_625x300_17_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-delhis-aqi-was-494-today-but-international-monitor-said-1600-7054945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi's%20air%20quality%20remained%20severely%20toxic%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20the%20overall%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%2C%20which%20measures%20pollutants%2C%20spiked%20to%20494.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Companies%20say%20RTO%20mandates%20make%20work%20more%20creative%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20it%20might%20take%20more%20than%20that%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226437%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20coworkers%20greet%20a%20fellow%20staff%20member%20while%20returning%20to%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5