if%20it%20chooses%20to%20shift%20semiconductor%20policy%20from%20subsidies%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-tariffs-chips-could-create-more-american-jobs-increase-prices-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20Commerce%20Department%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20finalized%20CHIPS%20Act%20agreements%20are%20binding%20contracts%3A%20After%20an%20agreement%20is%20finalized%2C%20the%20funding%20can't%20be%20rescinded%20unless%20the%20company%20fails%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20deal.%20Absent%20that%2C%20they%20said%20rescinding%20funding%20would%20require%20an%20act%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fepisode%2F0e9ynAH6hmZIIeOx0SaGQu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20podcaster%20Joe%20Rogan%20in%20October%2C%20Trump%20said%20tariffs%20would%20have%20been%20a%20better%20way%20to%20motivate%20chipmakers%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20US.%20And%20in%20November%2C%20House%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20said%20Republicans%20may%20try%20to%20modify%20the%20CHIPS%20Act%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eby%20removing%20certain%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F11%2F01%2Fpolitics%2Fjohnson-chips-act%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecostly%20regulations%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20environmental%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20%26quot%3Bwill%20implement%20the%20promises%20he%20made%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%26quot%3B%20Karoline%20Leavitt%2C%20Trump-Vance%20transition%20spokeswoman%2C%20told%20BI.%20However%2C%20she%20did%20not%20answer%20questions%20about%20whether%20Trump's%20approach%20to%20CHIPS%20Act%20funding%20could%20differ%20from%20that%20of%20the%20Biden%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Koch%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20the%20semiconductor%20research%20and%20consulting%20firm%20SemiAnalysis%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that