tic%20about%20the%20future%20landscape%20for%20space%20companies%2C%20given%20early%20indicators%20of%20the%20administration's%20sharper%20focus%20on%20space%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20space%20does%20well%2C%20we%20do%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Beck%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Rocket%20Lab%2C%20competing%20with%20SpaceX%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20David-and-Goliath%20dynamic.%20One%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20startups%2C%20SpaceX%20was%20last%20valued%20at%20%24210%20billion.%20Rocket%20Lab%20is%20valued%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20that%2C%20with%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20around%20%249.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20faze%20Beck.%20The%20CEO%20recounted%20when%20Virgin%20Orbit%2C%20which%20invested%20around%20%241.2%20billion%20in%20getting%20its%20first%20rocket%20into%20orbit%2C%20was%20expected%20to%20win%20the%20small%20launch%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20%241.1%20billion%20more%20than%20we%20spent%2C%26quot%3B%20Beck%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-orbit-bankruptcy-richard-branson-rocket-firm-files-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVirgin%20Orbit%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20April%202023.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20Rocket%20Lab%20acquired%20one%20of%20Virgin%20Orbit's%20facilities%20in%20a%20bankruptcy%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElectron%2C%20Rocket%20Lab's%20partially%20reusable%20two-stage%20rocket%20vehicle%20that%20has%20launched%20198%20satellites%2C%20beat%20Jeff%20Bezos'%20Blue%20Origin%20to%20orbit%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-impressed-rocket-lab-ceo-beat-jeff-bezos-orbit-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%20once%20told%20his%20biographer%20was%20%26quot%3Bimpressive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeck%20said%20that%20while%20%26quot%3Bmoney%20is%20certainly%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20success%20is%20about%20