nistry%20called%20for%20senior%20company%20executives%20to%20meet%20Minister%20Agus%20Gumiwang%20Kartasasmita.%20But%20after%20flying%20into%20Jakarta%2C%20Apple's%20senior%20executives%20were%20told%20that%20the%20minister%20wasn't%20available%20and%20so%20they%20had%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20ministry's%20director-general%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Industry%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20new%20investment%20proposal%20came%20after%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Industry%20last%20month%20blocked%20sales%20of%20the%20iPhone%2016%20on%20the%20grounds%20the%20US%20company's%20local%20unit%20hasn't%20met%20a%2040%25%20domestic%20content%20requirement%20for%20smartphones%20and%20tablets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Indonesian%20government%2C%20Apple%20has%20only%20invested%201.5%20trillion%20rupiah%20(%2495%20million)%20in%20the%20nation%20via%20developer%20academies%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20a%20commitment%20of%201.7%20trillion%20rupiah.%20The%20Southeast%20Asian%20nation%20has%20also%20banned%20the%20sale%20of%20Alphabet%20Inc.'s%20Google%20Pixel%20phones%20because%20of%20a%20similar%20lack%20of%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia's%20hardball%20tactics%20appear%20to%20be%20working%2C%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016%20ban%20becoming%20an%20example%20of%20the%20pressure%20new%20President%20Prabowo%20Subianto's%20government%20is%20putting%20on%20international%20firms%20to%20increase%20local%20manufacturing%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20boost%20domestic%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20also%20resorted%20to%20such%20tactics%20under%20the%20administration%20of%20former%20President%20Joko%20Widodo%2C%20who%20blocked%20ByteDance%20Ltd.'s%20TikTok%20last%20year%20to%20shield%20its%20retail%20sector%20from%20cheap%20Chinese-made%20goods.%20This%20prompted%20the%20hugely%20popular%20video%20app%20to%20ultimately%20invest%20%241.5%20billion%20in%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Tokopedia%2C%20the%20e-commerce%20arm%20of%20Indonesia's%20GoTo%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Apple%20is%20seeking%20to%20get%20unfettered%20access%20to%20Indonesia's%20278%20million%20consumers%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20which%20are%20under%20the%20age%20of%2044%20and%20tech%20savvy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20strong-arm%20tactics%20by%20Indonesia%20risk%20frightening%20off%20other%20firms%20from%20scaling%20up%20their%20presence%20or%20establishing%20a%20footprint%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20particularly%20ones%20that%20are%20looking%20to%20decouple%20from%20China.%20It%20may%20also%20jeopardize%20Prabowo's%20aim%20of%20attracting%20overseas%20investments%20to%20grow%20the%20economy%20and%20fund%20policy%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20as%20to%20which%20companies%20Apple's%20proposed%20investment%20might%20go.%20Apple%20typically%20backs%20assembly%20or%20components%20partners%20such%20as%20Foxconn%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20help%20produce%20or%20supply%20vital%20parts%20for%20its%20iPhones%20and%20iPads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732004220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F19eei8do_iphone-16-pro_625x300_18_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-offers-100-million-to-undo-indonesia-iphone-16-ban-7054273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20Inc.%20has%20increased%20its%20offer%20to%20invest%20in%20Indonesia%20by%20almost%20tenfold%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20in%20the%20US%20tech%20giant's%20latest%20bid%20to%20persuade%20the%20government%20to%20lift%20its%20sales%20ban%20on%20the%20iPhone%2016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2