eing%20has%20rapidly%20become%20the%20celebration%20of%20choice%20across%20the%20US%20sporting%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20blood-soaked%20Ultimate%20Fighting%20Championship%20to%20the%20hard-hitting%20National%20Football%20League%20and%20the%20reliably%20decorous%20world%20of%20the%20LPGA%20Tour%20golf%2C%20athletes%20across%20North%20America%20have%20succumbed%20to%20the%20viral%20Trump%20dance%20craze%20in%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20United%20States%20soccer%20star%20Christian%20Pulisic%20became%20the%20latest%20exponent%20of%20what%20might%20be%20called%20'the%20Donald'%2C%20rushing%20to%20the%20sideline%20with%20several%20team-mates%20to%20mimic%20the%20US%20President-elect's%20signature%2C%20fist-pumping%20shuffle%20after%20scoring%20his%20team's%20opening%20goal%20in%20a%204-2%20win%20over%20Jamaica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20prominent%20example%20came%20at%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20on%20Saturday%2C%20when%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20fighter%20Jon%20Jones%20knocked%20out%20Stipe%20Miocic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Trump%20just%20a%20few%20feet%20away%20at%20ringside%2C%20Jones%20quickly%20broke%20out%20an%20unmistakeable%20hip-swinging%20rendition%20of%20the%20Republican%20leader's%20dance%20before%20presenting%20Trump%20with%20his%20heavyweight%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20countless%20other%20examples%20across%20the%20NFL%20and%20collegiate%20gridiron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Francisco%2049ers'%20Nick%20Bosa%20--%20who%20drew%20criticism%20for%20crashing%20a%20postgame%20interview%20wearing%20a%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%26quot%3B%20baseball%20cap%20shortly%20before%20the%20US%20election%20on%20November%205%20--%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20NFL%20players%20to%20do%20the%20dance%20after%20sacking%20an%20opponent%20on%20November%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20guys%20wanted%20me%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bosa%20told%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Chronicle.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20even%20going%20to%20do%20it%2C%20but%20the%20boys%20reminded%20me.%20And%20it%20was%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBosa%20was%20coy%20however%20when%20asked%20who%20his%20dance%20had%20been%20inspired%20by.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20know%20the%20answer%20to%20that%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20most%20recent%20NFL%20Sunday%2C%20several%20players%20adopted%20the%20celebration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20was%20Las%20Vegas%20Raiders%20tight%20end%20Brock%20Bowers%2C%20who%20busted%20out%20the%20Trump%20moves%20after%20scoring%20a%20touchdown%20in%20his%20team's%20defeat%20to%20the%20Miami%20Dolphins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBowers%20said%20the%20move%20was%20prompted%20by%20UFC%20fighter%20Jones'%20celebration%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20everyone%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowers%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20watched%20the%20UFC%20fight%20last%20night%20and%20Jon%20Jones%20did%20it.%20I%20like%20watching%20UFC%20so%20I%20saw%20it%20and%20thought%20it%20was%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20media%20reports%20said%20Raiders%20team%20officials%20abruptly%20shut%20down%20Bowers'%20availability%20following%20the%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Florida%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Trump%20dance%20had%20even%20reached%20women's%20golf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland's%20Charley%20Hull%20jokingly%20performed%20the%20move%20as%20she%20walked%20down%20the%20fairway%20in%20her%20final%20round%20duel%20with%20Nelly%20Korda%20at%20the%20Annika%20tournament%20at%20Pelican%20Golf%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20international%20soccer%20player%20and%20television%20pundit%20Alexi%20Lalas%20couldn't%20hide%20his%20delight%20after%20Pulisic%20got%20in%20on%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPulisic%20scores.%20Pulisic%20does%20the%20Trump%20dance.%20We're%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup...bigly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrot