esofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsydney-trains-set-to-shut-down-from-november-21-22-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F115441663.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsydney-trains-set-to-shut-down-from-november-21-22-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F115441663.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Quietly%20Discontinues%20This%20Popular%20iPhone%20Accessory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20appears%20to%20have%20quietly%20phased%20out%20one%20of%20its%20long-standing%20accessories%2C%20the%203.5mm%20lightning%20to%20headphone%20jack%20adapter.%20The%20adapter%2C%20which%20allowed%20users%20to%20connect%20wired%20headphones%20and%20other%20audio%20devices%20to%20iPhones%20that%20lack%20a%20headphone%20jack%2C%20has%20been%20listed%20as%20%E2%80%9Csold%20out%E2%80%9D%20on%20Apple's%20online%20store%20in%20the%20US%20and%20most%20other%20countries%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2024%2F11%2F17%2Flightning-to-headphone-jack-adapter-sold-out%2F%5C%22%3EMacRumors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Apple%20decided%20to%20discontinue%20the%203.5mm%20headphone%20port%20from%20the%20iPhone%207%2C%20the%20Lightning%20to%203.5mm%20Adapter%20made%20its%20debut%20in%202016.%20This%20move%20left%20many%20users%20needing%20a%20solution%20for%20their%20existing%20wired%20headphones%2C%20which%20were%20no%20longer%20compatible%20with%20the%20new%20models.%20The%20adapter%20offered%20a%20simple%20fix%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20continue%20using%20their%20wired%20headphones%20without%20switching%20to%20Bluetooth%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20away%20from%20the%20Lightning%20connector%20gained%20further%20momentum%20with%20the%20release%20of%20the%20iPhone%2015%20in%202023%2C%20which%20officially%20adopted%20USB-C.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20adapter%20was%20bundled%20with%20new%20iPhone%20models%20from%20the%20iPhone%207%20through%20to%20the%20iPhone%20XS%2C%20released%20in%202018.%20But%20by%20then%2C%20many%20users%20had%20already%20shifted%20to%20wireless%20solutions%20like%20Apple's%20Lightning%20EarPods%20or%20Bluetooth%20AirPods%2C%20and%20the%20adapter%20was%20no%20longer%20included%20in%20the%20box.%20It%20continued%20to%20be%20available%20for%20purchase%20separately%20at%20Apple%20stores%2C%20but%20now%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20disappearing%20from%20the%20shelves%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F11%2F18%2Ftech%2Fapple-discontinues-popular-accessory-many-people-need%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20discontinuation%20appears%20to%20be%20part%20of%20Apple's%20broader%20transition%20away%20from%20its%20proprietary%20Lightning%20port%20in%20favour%20of%20USB-C%2C%20which%20has%20now%20become%20the%20standard%20for%20the%20company's%20newer%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20adapter%20has%20been%20discontinued%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20US%20and%20Australia%2C%20it%20is%20still%20available%20in%20France%2C%20Denmark%2C%20Finland%2C%20Norway%20and%20Sweden.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20found%20through%20third-party%20retailers%20such%20as%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732001580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F886jqpb_apple_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fapple-quietly-discontinues-this-popular-iphone-accessory-7053910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20appears%20to%20have%20quietly%20phased%20out%20one%20of%20its%20long-standing%20accessories%2C%20the%203.5mm%20lightning%20to%20headphone%20jack%20adapter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fapple-quietly-discontinues-this-popular-iphone-accessory-7053910%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22