news%2Fmarket-recovery-sensex-pops-1-113-pts-nifty-up-327-pts-top-reasons-here-124111900452_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Team%20Trump%3A%20There's%20Method%20To%20This%20Madness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fr92i04ro_donald-trump_625x300_07_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20U.S.%20presidential%20election%20defied%20expectations%2C%20delivering%20results%20that%20will%20shape%20American%20politics%20in%20unpredictable%20ways.%20For%20only%20the%20second%20time%20in%20US%20history%2C%20a%20president%20won%20non-consecutive%20terms%20in%20office.%20Despite%20widespread%20predictions%20of%20a%20contentious%20transition%2C%20the%20handover%20from%20President%20Biden%20to%20President%20Trump%20was%20remarkably%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20did%20more%20than%20simply%20return%20Trump%20to%20office%3B%20it%20also%20gave%20the%20Republican%20Party%20control%20over%20both%20chambers%20of%20Congress%2C%20completing%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrifecta%E2%80%9D%20of%20control%20across%20the%20executive%20and%20legislative%20branches.%20With%20this%20majority%2C%20Trump%20has%20moved%20quickly%20to%20form%20his%20cabinet%2C%20signalling%20his%20commitment%20to%20an%20assertive%2C%20and%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20radical%20policy%20direction.%20His%20cabinet%20picks%20have%20both%20reassured%20his%20base%20and%20stirred%20fresh%20controversy%20among%20Democrats%20and%20even%20some%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Complex%20Blend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20cabinet%20nominations%20have%20surprised%20many%2C%20reflecting%20his%20intent%20to%20shake%20up%20the%20status%20quo%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20political%20loyalty%20and%20unconventional%20figures.%20His%20picks%20for%20Secretary%20of%20State%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%2C%20Senator%20Marco%20Rubio%20and%20Congressman%20Michael%20Waltz%2C%20respectively%2C%20have%20been%20met%20with%20cautious%20optimism.%20However%2C%20other%20nominations%20have%20sparked%20bipartisan%20concern.%20Trump's%20choice%20of%20Pete%20Hegseth%20as%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20signal%20of%20a%20conservative%20re-evaluation%20of%20the%20military's%20role%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20structure.%20Known%20for%20his%20hawkish%20views%2C%20Hegseth%20is%20expected%20to%20push%20for%20a%20downsized%20but%20more%20targeted%20military%20approach%2C%20potentially%20bringing%20resources%20from%20long-standing%20international%20deployments%20to%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20controversial%20decision%20is%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20appoint%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%20as%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence.%20Gabbard%2C%20a%20former%20Democratic%20Congresswoman%20known%20for%20her%20anti-interventionist%20stance%2C%20has%20drawn%20scrutiny%20due%20to%20her%20critiques%20of%20US%20military%20actions%20abroad%20and%20her%20relatively%20diplomatic%20tone%20toward%20adversaries%20like%20Syria's%20Bashar%20al-Assad.%20Her%20stance%20on%20foreign%20interventions%20may%20face%20significant%20resistance%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Some%20Names%20Have%20Raised%20Eyebrows%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20choices%20for%20domestic%20policy%20roles%20have%20provoked%20an%20even%20stronger%20backlash.%20His%20selection%20of%20Matt%20Gaetz%20as%20Attorney%20General%20and%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20as%20Secretary%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20has%20ignited%20concerns%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum.%20Gaetz%2C%20a%20controversial%20figure%20with%20ongoing%20legal%20issues%2C%20is%20perceived%20by%20critics%20as%20an%20overly%20polarising%20choice%20to%20lead%20the%20Justice%20Department.%20Similarly%2C%20Kennedy%2C%20known%20for%20his%20outspoken%20opposition%20to%20vaccines%2C%20raises%20questions%20about%20his%20suitability%20to%20lead%20a%20department%20overseeing%20national%20health%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20establishment%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%2C%20led%20by%20high-profile%20entrepreneurs%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20and%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20been%20met%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20enthusiasm%20and%20scepticism.%20While%20the%20concept%20of%20streamlining%20government%20operations%20and%20reducing%20bureaucracy%20is%20appealing%20to%20many%2C%20the%20feasibility%20of%20such%20an%20initiative%20remains%20uncertain.%20DOGE's%20role%20is%20intended%20to%20be%20primarily%20domestic%2C%20targeting%20inefficiencies%20in%20agencies%20like%20the%20Department%20of%20State%20and%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20which%20are%20often%20criticised%20for%20sluggish%20operations.%20Yet%2C%20some%20fear%20that%20drastic%20cuts%20or%20restructuring%20could%20disrupt%20government%20functions%2C%20creating%20bottlenecks%20rather%20than%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20these%20appointments%2C%20there%20is%20growing%20speculation%20that%20Trump%20is%20prioritising%20loyalty%20over%20qualifications.%20Some%20Republicans%20have%20privately%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20certain%20nominees%20may%20struggle%20to%20pass%20Senate%20confirmation%2C%20even%20with%20the%20party's%20majority.%20This%20scenario%20would%20put%20Trump%20in%20a%20delicate%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fringe%20Rules%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%2C%20for%20their%20part%2C%20have%20criticised%20Trump's%20cabinet%20selections%2C%20suggesting%20that%20his%20administration%20risks%20becoming%20insular%2C%20filled%20with%20figures%20from%20the%20political%20fringe.%20They%20warn%20that%20governing%20with%20a%20small%2C%20ideologically%20close%20circle%20could%20be%20the%20worst%20sounding%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20controversies%2C%20Trump's%20nominations%20for%20Rubio%2C%20Waltz%2C%20and%20Hegseth%20indicate%20a%20clear%20intent%20to%20strengthen%20America's%20role%20abroad%20through%20a%20resolute%20foreign%20policy.%20His%20administration%20appears%20focused%20on%20standing%20firm%20against%20rivals%20like%20China%2C%20reinforcing%20traditional%20alliances%2C%20and%20avoiding%20new%20military%20conflicts.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Trump's%20administration%20seems%20inclined%20to%20reduce%20military%20entanglements%20in%20ongoing%20wars%2C%20in%20line%20with%20his%20campaign%20promises%20to%20prioritise%20American%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20presidency%20could%20mark%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20US-India%20relations.%20Rubio%20and%20Waltz%20are%20both%20strong%20proponents%20of%20closer%20US-India%20ties%2C%20viewing%20the%20partnership%20as%20crucial%20for%20countering%20China's%20influence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20Above%20all%2C%20Trump's%20personal%20rapport%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20adds%20guardrails%20of%20certainty%20to%20the%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump's%20choices%20reflect%20his%20desire%20for%20a%20loyal%20team%2C%20they%20also%20signal%20his%20intention%20to%20challenge%20traditional%20governance%20structures%20and%20pursue%20a%20different%20vision%20for%20America's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V%20Pant%20is%20Vice%20President%20for%20Studies%20at%20ORF%20and%20Professor%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20Vivek%20Mishra%20is%20Fellow%2C%20Americas%2C%20at%20ORF.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20authors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731999240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fr92i04ro_donald-trump_625x300_07_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A