ues%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20picture%20was%20taken%20too%20soon%2C%20as%20Biden%20was%20still%20making%20his%20way%20to%20the%20area%20from%20talks%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20took%20the%20photo%20early%20before%20all%20the%20leaders%20had%20arrived.%20So%20a%20number%20of%20the%20leaders%20weren't%20actually%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20US%20official%20said%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20and%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20also%20missed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden's%20Twilight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20issue%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20a%20deliberate%20snub%2C%20it%20reflected%20the%20increasingly%20sidelined%20status%20of%20the%20lame-duck%20US%20leader%20as%20Trump's%20comeback%20looms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20the%20leaders%20of%20three%20BRICS%20countries%20in%20the%20front%20row%20that%20see%20themselves%20as%20a%20counterpart%20to%20a%20Western-dominated%20world%20did%20not%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%2C%20US%20officials%20played%20down%20footage%20of%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20and%20most%20powerful%20military%20apparently%20straying%20from%20the%20red%20carpet%20on%20the%20way%20into%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20officials%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bseveral%26quot%3B%20leaders%20from%20%26quot%3Bcountries%20that%20face%20high%20threats%26quot%3B%20took%20a%20different%20route%20like%20Biden%20did%2C%20even%20if%20Brazilian%20media%20said%20they%20did%20not%20see%20any%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20missteps%20come%20in%20the%20twilight%20of%20a%20presidency%20whose%20achievements%20are%20set%20to%20meet%20a%20Trump-shaped%20wrecking%20ball%20come%20January%2020th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20against%20Trump%20after%20a%20disastrous%20debate%20raised%20concerns%20about%20his%20age%2C%20but%20he%20still%20saw%20his%20Democratic%20replacement%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20lose%20heavily%20to%20the%20Republican.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20his%20six-day%20tour%20of%20South%20America%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20desperate%20frenzy%20to%20reassure%20world%20leaders%20amid%20uncertainty%20about%20what%20Trump%20will%20bring%2C%20from%20trade%20wars%20to%20threats%20to%20upending%20old%20alliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinal%20Pitch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20G20%20on%20Monday%2C%20Biden%20had%20urged%20the%20other%20leaders%20to%20back%20Ukraine's%20%26quot%3Bsovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20first%20comments%20since%20it%20emerged%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20had%20approved%20Kyiv's%20use%20of%20long-range%20missiles%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20Trump%20could%20reverse%20not%20only%20that%20decision%2C%20but%20also%20Biden's%20huge%20US%20military%20aid%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20signs%20that%20the%20president-elect%20may%20push%20through%20a%20peace%20deal%20that%20could%20force%20Kyiv%20to%20cede%20territory%20to%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20also%20pushed%20G20%20leaders%20to%20pressure%20Hamas%20on%20a%20ceasefire%20deal%20with%20Israel%20--%20and%20while%20Trump%20has%20appointed%20some%20key%20Israel%20hawks%2C%20he%20may%20also%20try%20to%20push%20for%20a%20historic%20deal%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20and%20again%2C%20Biden%20has%20used%20his%20valedictory%20appearance%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20to%20try%20to%20keep%20his%20policies%20out%20of%20Trump's%20shadow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20summit%20in%20Lima%20last%20week%2C%20Biden%20met%20with%20Xi%2C%20who%20promised%20to%20work%20with%20Trump%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmooth%26quot%3B%20transition%20even%20as%20both%20leaders%20warned%20of%20turbulence%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20B