%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20noticeable%20uptick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20users%20on%20Bluesky%20have%20been%20publicly%20praising%20the%20site's%20similarity%20to%20%26quot%3Bold%20Twitter%2C%26quot%3B%20complete%20with%20a%20reverse%20chronological%20timeline%2C%20less%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-visits-auschwitz-amid-uproar-over-antisemitic-messages-x-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehate%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20misinformation%2C%20and%20more%20control%20over%20what%20content%20is%20shown%20in%20your%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20growth%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20snowball.%20Social%20media%20researchers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20users%2C%20for%20fear%20of%20missing%20out%2C%20often%20wait%20to%20change%20their%20digital%20habits%20until%20new%20social%20sites%20demonstrate%20there's%20frequent%20enough%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20relevant%20%E2%80%94%20activity%20on%20the%20platform%20to%20join%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20new%20pull%20toward%20Bluesky%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20platform%20finally%20tapping%20into%20that%20%26quot%3Bnetwork%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20Bellack%2C%20the%20director%20of%20Harvard's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasml.cyber.harvard.edu%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApplied%20Social%20Media%20Lab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Enough%20people%20now%20seem%20to%20have%20joined%20the%20site%20to%20reach%20a%20critical%20mass%2C%20so%20users%20don't%20feel%20like%20they're%20missing%20out%20on%20content%20on%20other%20platforms%20or%20losing%20their%20online%20community%20by%20switching%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20helps%20when%20the%20people%20who%20make%20the%20switch%20have%20some%20social%20capital%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHello%20Less%20Hateful%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Cuban%2C%20the%20billionaire%20entrepreneur%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fmcuban.bsky.social%2Fpost%2F3laqxchlxvw2e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eposted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Bluesky%20on%20Tuesday%20last%20week%2C%20announcing%20that%20he'd%20made%20it%20his%20new%20primary%20social%20media%20platform.%20While%20still%20somewhat%20active%20on%20X%2C%20Cuban%20has%20reposted%20lists%20of%20users%20he%20recommends%20following%20on%20Bluesky%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20an%20effort%20to%20rebuild%20his%20social%20media%20community%20on%20the%20new%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Cuban%20said%20he%20likes%20Bluesky%20better%20than%20the%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20variety%20of%20content%20and%20engagement%20is%20improving%20daily%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20different%20verticals%20are%20filling%20out%20as%20sources%20of%20news%20and%20information%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20said%20Threads%20%26quot%3Balso%20has%20value.%26quot%3B%20So%20he'll%20be%20posting%20there%2C%20too%2C%20but%20he'll%20prioritize%20Bluesky%20going%20forward.%20The%20Cost%20Plus%20Drugs%20cofounder%20has%208.9%20million%20followers%20on%20X%2C%20659%2C000%20on%20Threads%2C%20and%20384%2C700%20on%20Bluesky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20X%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22111f5e87-99fe-4c84-936d-4cefab40255c%5C%22%3EHow%20Bluesky%20compares%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEstimates%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.similarweb.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESimilarweb%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20digital%20market%20intelligence%20company%2C%20said%20daily%20active%20users%20of%20the%20Bluesky%20mobile%20app%20in%20the%20US%20increased%2073%25%20the%20week%20after%20the%20election%2C%20rising%2040%25%20more%20%E2%80%94%20to%202.6%20million%20daily%20users%20%E2%80%94%20by%20the%20following%20Thursday.%20That's%20compared%20to%2031.2%20million%20for%20X%20and%204.3%20million%20for%20Threads%20in%20the%20same%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%2C%20which%20owns%20Threads%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20platform%20has%20seen%20more%20than%2015%20million%20signups%20in%20November%2C%20with%20more%20than%20one%20million%20signups%20per%20day%20for%20almost%20three%20months.%20The%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20the%20company%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bpleased%20to%20see%20Threads'%20steady%20growth%20since%20it%20launched%20last%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Meta's%20sprawling%2C%20interconnected%20brand%20has%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20muddied%26quot%3B%20Threads'%20appeal%20to%20users%20who%20are%20turning%20toward%20decentralized%20social%20media%2C%20said%20Stephen%20Lind%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20business%20communication%20at%20USC%20Marshall%20School%20of%20Business.%20That%20may%20be%20a%20reason%20Similarweb%20found%20Bluesky%20drew%20in%20more%20traffic%20than%20Threads%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.similarweb.com%2Fblog%2Finsights%2Fsocial-media-news%2Fx-traffic-peak-deactivations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EData%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Similarweb%20indicates%20Election%20Day%20also%20saw%20a%20surge%20of%20deactivations%20on%20X%2C%20with%20more%20than%20280%2C000%20people%20closing%20their%20accounts%20worldwide%20in%20a%20single%20day.%20Research%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsensortower.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESensor%20Tower%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20market%20intelligence%20firm%2C%20shows%20X's%20daily%20active%20users%20have%20stayed%20flat%20since%20the%20election%2C%20while%20Threads'%20jumped%208%25%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20Bluesky's%20more%20than%20119%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELind%20said%20Bluesky%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20a%20compelling%20alternative%26quot%3B%20to%20X%2C%20especially%20for%20users%20who%20don't%20appreciate%20Musk's%20approach%20to%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%2C%20time%20and%20time%20again%2C%20show%20us%20that%20they%20will%20put%20a%20brand%20in%20jeopardy%20if%20the%20leadership%20is%20associated%20with%20ideology%20the%20consumers%20don't%20care%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Lind%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20catch%20is%2C%20though%2C%20that%20for%20many%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20viable%20alternative%2C%20or%20that%20principled%20behavior%20sometimes%20takes%20a%20backseat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Bluesky%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20platform%20aims%20to%20give%20users%20more%20choice%20and%20offer%20creators%20independence%20from%20being%20locked%20into%20specific%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clear%20that%20people%20want%20an%20open%20and%20transparent%20social%20network%20that%20puts%20users%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bluesky%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20heard%20from%20users%20that%20they're%20receiving%20incredibly%20high%20levels%20of%20engagement%20from%20real%20people%2C%20and%20that%20most%20importantly%2C%20they're%20having%20fun%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226b20535-ac0f-465e-84ae-931c90a46c72%5C%22%3EChallenges%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20is%20switching.%20Advertisers%20are%20still%20noticeably%20absent%20from%20both%20Threads%20and%20Bluesky%2C%20and%20the%20similarities%20to%20pre-Musk%20Twitter%20aren't%20a%20selling%20point%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Dorsey%2C%20who%20co-founded%20both%20platforms%2C%20said%20in%20May%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20Bluesky%20because%20it%20was%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-dorsey-bluesky-twiiter-nostr-interview-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20much%20like%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bliterally%20repeating%20all%20the%20mistakes%26q