mers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20vision%20for%20Alexa%20is%20to%20build%20the%20world's%20best%20personal%20assistant.%20Generative%20AI%20offers%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20to%20make%20Alexa%20even%20better%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20and%20we%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20enable%20even%20more%20proactive%20and%20capable%20assistance%20on%20the%20over%20half%20a%20billion%20Alexa-enabled%20devices%20already%20in%20homes%20around%20the%20world.%20We%20are%20excited%20about%20what%20we're%20building%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20delivering%20it%20for%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Uber%2C%20Ticketmaster%2C%20Vagaro%2C%20OpenTable%2C%20Grubhub%2C%20Instacart%2C%20Fodors%2C%20and%20Thumbtack%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290c1aa42-4f32-4431-8ed8-40c8b40b4453%5C%22%3ERe-architecting%20%26quot%3Bthe%20brains%20of%20Alexa%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPotential%20integrations%20with%20these%20partner%20companies%20are%20important%20for%20Amazon%20because%20completing%20entire%20tasks%20for%20users%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20new%20Alexa's%20value%20proposition.%20An%20internal%20product%20description%2C%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20paints%20a%20picture%20of%20an%20advanced%20AI%20assistant%20capable%20of%20handling%20many%20types%20of%20user%20inquiries%20through%20multiple%20channels%2C%20not%20just%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20hopes%20the%20AI%20update%20will%20reignite%20interest%20in%20Alexa.%20The%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-alexa-job-layoffs-rise-and-fall-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificantly%20cut%20back%20on%20Alexa%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20after%20the%20voice-assistant%20failed%20to%20establish%20a%20profitable%20business%20model.%20Some%20Amazon%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-paid