lth.%20By%20keeping%20grasshopper%20populations%20in%20check%2C%20they%20also%20protect%20crops%2C%20promoting%20agricultural%20productivity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConserving%20sparrows%20is%20also%20essential%20for%20maintaining%20biodiversity%2C%20as%20they%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20seed%20dispersal.%20By%20feeding%20on%20seeds%20from%20various%20plants%2C%20sparrows%20help%20spread%20plant%20species%20across%20ecosystems%2C%20supporting%20the%20regeneration%20of%20plant%20life.%20This%20process%20not%20only%20promotes%20healthy%20and%20diverse%20habitats%20but%20also%20ensures%20the%20long-term%20stability%20of%20ecosystems%2C%20making%20sparrow%20conservation%20crucial%20for%20environmental%20balance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%E2%80%99s%20impact%20has%20been%20far-reaching.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Koodugal%20has%20distributed%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20nest%20boxes%20across%2040-45%20schools%20and%20gated%20communities%20in%20Chennai.%20According%20to%20Ganeshan%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%2060-70%25%20of%20the%20nest%20boxes%20are%20now%20occupied%20by%20sparrows%2C%20with%20multiple%20generations%20now%20nesting%20in%20the%20boxes.%20In%20North%20Chennai%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251443%2Fd-ganesan-chennai-professor-koodugal-trust-sparrow-nesting-space-conservation-sanctuary-school-student-volunteer-initiative-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esparrow%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20increased%20by%2015%25%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20ambitious%20venture%2C%20Koodugal%20Nest%20faced%20its%20share%20of%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20approached%20communities%20in%20North%20Chennai%2C%20people%20were%20hesitant.%20We%20were%20strangers%2C%20and%20many%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20sparrow%20conservation%20mattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20recalls.%20The%20team%20faced%20initial%20roadblocks%20in%20convincing%20local%20residents%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20organisations%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20we%20reached%20out%20to%20ten%20schools%20and%20gained%20media%20attention%2C%20schools%20began%20welcoming%20our%20projects%2C%20and%20soon%20both%2C%20educational%20institutions%20and%20local%20communities%20started%20actively%20engaging%20with%20us%20to%20promote%20sparrow%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganeshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20challenge%20was%20the%20cost%20of%20constructing%20the%20nest%20boxes.%20Initially%2C%20Koodugal%20worked%20with%20a%20carpenter%20who%20charged%20around%20Rs%20200-250%20per%20nest%20box.%20But%20the%20team%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20project%20more%20sustainable.%20To%20overcome%20this%2C%20they%20started%20producing%20their%20own%20kits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20get%20training%20to%20assemble%20sparrow%20nest%20boxes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-07-at-19.53.40-1-1731592109-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Im