thebetterindia.com%2F275250%2Fdelhi-nest-man-builds-bird-bamboo-homes-trains-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enest%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ensuring%20the%20continued%20growth%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20acknowledges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20communities%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20corporate%20partnerships%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20source%20of%20funding%2C%20Ganeshan%20stresses%20that%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20true%20success%20lies%20in%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20involvement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20impact%20comes%20from%20students%2C%20families%2C%20and%20communities%20coming%20together%20to%20make%20this%20project%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrevious%20generations%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20sparrows%2C%20but%20today%E2%80%99s%20generation%20is%20less%20aware%20of%20how%20vital%20they%20are%20for%20human%20survival.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20general%20public%20often%20lacks%20the%20time%20or%20interest%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20significance.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20schools%2C%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20explain%20the%20mission%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founder%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ganeshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.