xt%20generation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoodugal%20Trust%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20students.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20Prayukta%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20student%20from%20RPC%20Matriculation%20School%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20project%2C%20and%20he%20brought%20home%20a%20nest%20in%202022.%20We%20all%20helped%20in%20installing%20it%2C%20and%20it%20was%20amazing%20to%20watch%20sparrows%20take%20care%20of%20their%20young%20ones.%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20feeding%20them%20and%20observing%20their%20activities.%20I%20would%20love%20to%20continue%20this%20sparrow%20conservation%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20engaging%20students%20in%20hands-on%20projects%2C%20Koodugal%20is%20not%20only%20educating%20them%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%20but%20also%20improves%20their%20motor%20skills%2C%20concentration%2C%20and%20empathy.%20These%20activities%20have%20significantly%20reduced%20screen%20time%20and%20have%20helped%20children%20develop%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Ganeshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20future%20plans%2C%20Ganeshan%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20sparrows%20a%20common%20sight%20across%20Chennai%20and%20expand%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20project%20to%20more%20schools%20and%20gated%20communities.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20reach%201%2C00%2C000%20families%20and%20distribute%20more%20nest%20boxes%20in%2010%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20is%20also%20focusing%20on%20developing%20sparrow%20sanctuaries%20in%20more%20schools%2C%20where%20sparrows%20can%20nest%20and%20flourish%20in%20safe%2C%20protected%20environments.%20They%20have%20successfully%20established%20eight%20sparrow%20sanctuaries%20so%20far%2C%20providing%20a%20home%20for%20100%2